data.name: sqlDataSource1.SelectCommand
data.value:
SELECT Id, CustomerName, Comment, BelegunNumber, KundenNumber, LieferDatum, Rechnungsdatum, Varkaufer, IhreUID, Address, isnull(( SELECT count(MasterId) FROM Master_Credit_Grid1 where MasterId=M.Id and Beschreibung<>'' ),0) ch1cnt, isnull(( SELECT count(MasterId) FROM Master_Credit_Grid2 where MasterId=M.Id and Beschreibung<>'' ),0) ch2cnt, isnull(( SELECT count(MasterId) FROM Master_Credit_Grid3 where MasterId=M.Id and Beschreibung<>'' ),0) ch3cnt
FROM Master_Credit M where Id=1
